<p>For our recipes you can use any gluten free flour.  Personally, I always keep in my pantry a mix of flours that I like for baking.</p>

<h2 id="ingredients">Ingredients</h2>

<ul>
  <li>3 cups of rice flour</li>
  <li>1 cups of cornstarch</li>
  <li>1/2 cup fo tapioca starch</li>
</ul>

<p>Keep it in an air-tight container.
Note: make sure that all your ingredients are gluten-free.</p>

